iority`\n\nThis should still cover the same active `FrameworkLogger` dynamic-access sites while avoiding the GraalVM Log4j 2 build-time feature failure. I did not run the Gradle test command locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05023f7eef464c290169f8d193126c8196814d97e1c2f2c672\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1304, "output": 999, "cacheRead": 45056, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 47359, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777914246686, "responseId": "resp_05023f7eef464c290169f8d187907c81968f5589d8826f57db"}}
